'''賽吉出版公司'''（{{lang|en|Sage Publications}}）是由{{Link-en|莎拉·米勒·麥克卡尼|Sara Miller McCune}}在1965年成立於美國[[紐約|紐約]]的{{Link-en|獨立企業|Independent business|獨立}}[[出版社|出版公司]]。賽吉旗下約1,500名員工來自世界各地，在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]、[[倫敦|倫敦]]、[[新德里|新德里]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]及[[華盛頓哥倫比亞特區|華盛頓哥倫比亞特區]]均設有主要的辦事處。賽吉出版計劃包括700種期刊及超過800種書籍、<ref>{{cite web|title=Sage Publications|url=http://www.ipg.uk.com/cgi-bin/scribe?showinfo=pp132|work=Sage at a glance|publisher=Sage Publications|accessdate=2012-04-13|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414115757/http://www.ipg.uk.com/cgi-bin/scribe?showinfo=pp132|archivedate=2012-04-14}}</ref> 參考書，及每年在商業、人文、社會科學、科學、技術，及醫學等的電子書。

賽吉亦擁有及以下四個出版社：科溫出版社<ref>{{cite web|title=Sage Imprints|url=http://www.Sagepub.in/about/imprints.asp|work=Sage Imprints Page|publisher=Sage Publications|accessdate=2012-05-01|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070304215308/https://www.sagepub.in/about/imprints.asp|archivedate=2007-03-04}}</ref>（{{lang|en|Corwin}}，1990年創立），{{Link-en|CQ出版社|CQ Press}}<ref name=CQPress>{{cite web |url=http://www.alacrastore.com/deal-snapshot/Sage_Publications_USA_acquires_CQ_Press_from_Times_Publishing_Co-504314 |title=Sage Publications USA acquires CQ Press from Times Publishing Co — May 30, 2008 - M&A Deal Snapshot |format= |work=AlacraStore.com |accessdate=2010-08-08 |language=en |archive-date=2012-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120318001701/http://www.alacrastore.com/deal-snapshot/Sage_Publications_USA_acquires_CQ_Press_from_Times_Publishing_Co-504314 |dead-url=no }}</ref>（2008年創立）、學習事宜出版社（{{lang|en|Learning Matters}}，2011年創立)，<ref>{{cite web|title=Sage acquires Learning Matters|url=http://www.thebookseller.com/news/Sage-buys-learning-matters.html|work=''The Bookseller''|accessdate=2012-04-13|language=en|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107112519/http://www.thebookseller.com/news/sage-buys-learning-matters.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>及{{Link-en|亞當馬修數位出版社|Adam Matthew Digital}}（2012年創立）。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://reviews.libraryjournal.com/2012/10/reference/sage-acquires-adam-matthew/|title = SAGE Acquires Adam Matthew|date = 2012-10-11|accessdate = |website = Reviews|publisher = ''Library Journal''|last = Verma|first = Henrietta|language = en|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180618175710/https://reviews.libraryjournal.com/2012/10/reference/sage-acquires-adam-matthew/|archive-date = 2018-06-18|dead-url = yes}}</ref>
